channel.title: Comments on: The Faint – 9:30 Club – Washington, DC (12.5.12)

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: Blank Wave Arcade still blows my mind. I wanted to make a record like that back in '95 and nearly 20 years later I couldn't fathom executing as well as they did. It's just perfect.
item.content:encoded: Blank Wave Arcade still blows my mind. I wanted to make a record like that back in ’95 and nearly 20 years later I couldn’t fathom executing as well as they did. It’s just perfect.
